OL,6,FAccording to Parliament's Register of
OL,7,FMembers' Financial Interests, some MPs
OL,8,Fwho have extra responsibilities within
OL,9,Ftheir council are receiving as much as
OL,10,F#15,000 a year.
OL,12,FTwo Liberal Democrat MPs are also
OL,13,Fsitting on more than one council and
OL,14,Fgetting paid for both. Will Forster
OL,15,Fsits on both Surrey County Council and
OL,16,FWoking Borough Council, while James
OL,17,FMacCleary represents areas in East
OL,18,FSussex Council Council and Lewes
OL,19,FDistrict Council.
