OL,6,F'It's a balancing act': Streeting on
OL,7,FMPs doing both jobs
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting, who
OL,10,Fserved as a councillor himself
OL,11,Falongside being an MP when he was
OL,12,Ffirst elected, said it can be a good
OL,13,Fthing to do both jobs.
OL,15,F"This is a bit of a tricky one... I
OL,16,Fdid both jobs effectively, I didn't
OL,17,Fclaim a councillor's allowance," he
OL,18,Ftold ITV News.
