OL,6,F"To be honest, a lot of my
OL,7,Fconstituency casework now as an MP,
OL,8,Fand as a Cabinet minister is still
OL,9,Fabout local council services.
OL,11,F"There's such an overlap between the
OL,12,Ftwo roles, and you always have to
OL,13,Fweigh up the pros and cons of causing
OL,14,Fa by-election with the cost and
OL,15,Fdisruption that involves, or seeing
OL,16,Fout your term but accepting you might
OL,17,Fnot be able to make all of your
OL,18,Fcommittees.
