OL,6,F"What I wouldn't want to see is a
OL,7,Fsituation where councillors felt,
OL,8,Fbecause they're already elected, that
OL,9,Fthey couldn't also get elected to
OL,10,FParliament. Because I think it's a
OL,11,Fgood thing that we have people in
OL,12,Fparliament that have local government
OL,13,Fexperience."
OL,15,FA Liberal Democrat spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"Liberal Democrat MPs are committed to
OL,17,Fdelivering for their constituents day
OL,18,Fin day out. Those who are councillors
OL,19,Fwill take individual decisions on
OL,20,Fwhether to continue depending on their
OL,21,Flocal circumstances.
